          <title>McDavid makes perfect pass in overtime as the Oilers beat the Blackhawks 4-3</title>
          <description><![CDATA[CHICAGO (AP) — Connor McDavid set up Zach Hyman in overtime, and the Edmonton Oilers beat the Chicago Blackhawks 4-3 on Wednesday night. Hyman redirected McDavid's pass for the power-play goal at 1:36. It was Hyman's 19th goal and McDavid's 49th assist of the season.]]></description>
